1. 3 activities , 3 xml files
2. intents (explicit intents)

each activity -
    1. one question per page - question, choices, "submit" button
        on submit -> result and "next" button
    2. clicking "next" button -> takes you to another page with next question and
        [Step-1] Repeats
    3. once all questions are completed, show results (pass/fail) - activity - Result, Pass/Fail statement
